name: DailyJournalPrompts
0:
”Alexa, open journal prompts”
”Alexa, start journal prompts”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: journal prompts
des: Incorporate this into your self care routine to get to know yourself better and get inspired! Whether you are struggling with deciding what to write about or just want some new inspiration, this is the skill for you! Alexa will randomly choose a prompt for you to write about. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next prompt. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
